Hello Mr. Shodhan,

I don't know about the opinions of other volunteers who answer questions at the 
MathForum, but my opinion is that one should choose an angle that is pleasing 
aesthetically to you and let it go.  Why not use the angle in the Great Pyramid at Giza?


